In order to enter the URL of China Railway Customer Service Center or other website providing train information in the address bar of the browser, you need to click the address bar with the mouse first, and then enter the required website. The following are the JSON format operations required for this action:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 512, "height": 50}},
    {"action_type": "KeyboardAction", "keyboard_action_type": "text", "keyboard_text": "www.12306.cn"}
]
```
